red to be a crazy gamble, competing in the 5,000m, the 10,000m and the marathon - the last two events just two days apart.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9481070435437661, \"rank\": 0.049004029488012454, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crazy gamble\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5,000m\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two events\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in a thrilling sprint finish Hassan overhauled Ethiopia's Tigst Assefa to take gold by three seconds in an Olympic record of 2hr 22min 55sec.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9481070435437661, \"rank\": 0.049004029488012454, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999740217545147, \"rank\": 2.3409803993989686e-05, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a thrilling sprint\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"three seconds\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic record\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"2hr 22min 55sec\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday she had taken bronze in the 10,000m in Stade de France, after coming away with a bronze in the 5,000m.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000m\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5,000m.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She fell to the ground on the blue carpet in front of the golden dome of the Invalides memorial complex in the heart of Paris, before grabbing a Dutch flag to celebrate an extraordinary achievement.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.244625976281585e-27, \"text\": \"Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3562328490611214e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the blue carpet\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"the golden dome\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary achievement\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was not easy,\\\" said Hassan.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1081, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9481070435437661, \"rank\": 0.049004029488012454, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was so hot, but I was feeling okay.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never pushed myself through to the finish line as I did today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a sensational ending to an Olympics athletics programme that saw US sprinter Noah Lyles win the 100m by just five thousandths of a second.\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999993137862, \"rank\": 3.013463333796963e-10, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1285, \"end\": 1295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sensational endi